\n\r\nHere\'s the # that called you: [caller-id]<br /><br />\r\n    \r\nYou\'re getting this email with the caller ID shown<br />\r\nso you will know it came from someone who visited your<br />\r\nwebsite, and didn\'t just find you \'on the internet\'.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nCategorize the call, so at month\'s end, you\'ll have a<br />\r\nquick list that shows you what came in; for example:<br /><br />\r\n\r\nNew Potential Client<br />\r\nCurrent Client<br />\r\nPast Client<br />\r\nSolicitor<br />\r\nNon-Client Call<br />\r\n(judge, prosecutor, police, family)<br /><br />\r\n\r\nNot all calls are new potential clients, but I hope this<br />\r\none was and if so, that you retain them.<br /><br />\r\n\r\nRichard Jacobs<br />\r\nSpeakeasy Marketing, Inc.<br />\r\n(888) 225-8594 ph<br />\";s:8:\"bio_name\";s:23:\"Anitha W. Johnson, Esq.\";s:8:\"bio_list\";s:331:\"<li>Personalized & Dedicated Legal Representation</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Over 8 Years of Experience</li>\r\n\r\n<li><b>Member</b><br />\r\nMaryland State Bar Association\r\nThe District of Columbia Bar<br />\r\nDistrict of Columbia Trial Lawyers Association<br />\r\nMaryland Trial Lawyers Association<br />\r\nAmerican Immigration Lawyers Association</li>\";s:7:\"bio_img\";s:72:\"http://odelugojohnsonllc.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/bio_img-copy.png\";s:10:\"bio_name_2\";s:0:\"\";s:10:\"bio_list_2\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"bio_img_2\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"home_slider\";s:17:\"[rev_slider home]\";s:16:\"home_testimonial\";s:0:\"\";s:21:\"testimonial_link_text\";s:13:\"Read More >> \";s:12:\"book_title_1\";s:18:\"Surviving Divorce \";s:15:\"book_category_1\";s:20:\"Anitha W. Johnso Bio\";s:15:\"book_subtitle_1\";s:38:\"(Helpful Guide to  Navigate Your Case)\";s:9:\"book1_img\";s:67:\"http://odelugojohnsonllc.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/book_11.png\";s:9:\"book1_pdf\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"book_title_2\";s:26:\"Personal Injury Litigation\";s:15:\"book_category_2\";s:20:\"Anitha W. Johnso Bio\";s:15:\"book_subtitle_2\";s:38:\"(Helpful Guide