INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('804', '1', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Personal Injury and Auto Accident Attorneys</h2>\r\nAt Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, in Hyattsville, Maryland, we focus on the following areas of practice:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong> Motor vehicle accident </strong>  Following a car or truck accident, time is of the essence in securing representation and contacting the insurance company and a physician. From there, we do the hard work of advocating for you and resolving your case through negotiation, mediation or litigation.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Wrongful death </strong>  Resolving a case involving the loss of a loved one is complex and requires the experience of a seasoned attorney. We team up with various experts to estimate compensation due for your pain and suffering and lost income in the present and future.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Medical malpractice </strong>  If your doctor deviated from the basic standards of care in treating you, we can pursue a medical malpractice claim on your behalf. At Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, we will bring in medical experts to identify the problem and help us establish your claim.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Police brutality </strong>  Excessive force can cause serious injury and even death. It is also a violation of your civil rights. We will assist you throughout the entire process of filing and negotiating, or litigating a claim of police brutality.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Divorce and separation </strong>  Maryland and Washington, D.C. have their own laws. Our attorneys have an extensive knowledge of both jurisdictions and provide aggressive representation to clients from any area.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Child custody </strong>  Whether you are in Maryland or Washington, D.C., the focus in a child custody case is the best interests of the children. We work hard to ensure you get the time you need to continue to raise your child.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Child support </strong>  Child support involves strict calculations involving income, expenses and custody responsibilities. Most disputes concern the validity of the salary of one spouse and the true costs of daycare or health care.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Permanent residency and adjustment of status </strong>  Immigrants who enter the country legally need help in changing their status based on family matters or marriage. We encourage clients to apply immediately, as the process is lengthy.</li>\r\n	<li><strong> Business and family immigration </strong>  We help clients secure business visas for temporary or specialty employment that is in high demand. Our immigration attorneys also help family members with permanent residence status.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nIn addition to the above listed practice areas, we represent clients on slip and fall cases and protective orders.\r\n\r\nOur office is within walking distance from the metro. You may take the Green Line to Prince Georges Plaza. We are near Prince Georges Plaza Mall in the new development of University Town Center. We are accessible from the Beltway and Interstates 495 and 95 near Montgomery County and Washington, D.C. and free parking is available.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nFor more information or to schedule an appointment with an experienced personal injury, family law or immigration lawyer, please contact us.', 'Practice Areas Overview', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'practice-areas-overview', '', '', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '2014-02-28 05:42:43', '', '0', 'http://odelugojohnsonllc.com/?page_id=804', '0', 'page', '', '0');
