INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('809', '1', '2014-02-28 05:57:34', '2014-02-28 05:57:34', '<h2 id=\"areaFocus\">Maryland Wrongful Death and Fatal Accident Attorneys</h2>\r\nThe loss of a loved one is a devastating event in any familys life. If someone else\'s negligence resulted in your family members death, the lawyers at Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, in Hyattsville, Maryland, will work to hold the responsible individual or company <img class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-810\" alt=\"i-prac-wrongfuldeath\" src=\"http://odelugojohnsonllc.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/i-prac-wrongfuldeath.jpg\" width=\"214\" height=\"281\" />accountable.\r\n\r\nFar too many car accidents and instances of medical malpractice, nursing home neglect and police brutality have resulted in death. Everyone, from auto drivers to medical professionals, is required to exercise care for others\' safety.\r\n<h3>Seeking Justice Following a Wrongful Death</h3>\r\nWhen a fatality is due to foreseeable and preventable conduct, that only exacerbates the loss. At Odelugo &amp; Johnson, LLC, we provide a welcoming environment to our clients. That helps those who need an attorney to right a horrible wrong: the death of a family member. We have experience with wrongful death cases that resulted from motor vehicle accidents, medical malpractice and police brutality.\r\n<h3>Individuals and Professionals Causing a Wrongful Death</h3>\r\nDoctors are required to exercise basic standards of care. Police officers are supposed to use restraint, and respect suspects\' rights. Car and truck drivers must consider that others are on the road, at risk if they are inattentive, negligent or, worst of all, impaired by alcohol or drugs.\r\n<h3>Advocating for Your Wrongful Death Claim</h3>\r\nWhile you deal with the myriad emotions and the effects on your family, we will work diligently to establish your case and try to place a value on an unimaginable tragedy. That includes present and future lost wages if the deceased family member was a primary wage earner.\r\n\r\nOur office is within walking distance from the metro. You may take the Green Line to Prince Georges Plaza. We are near Prince Georges Plaza Mall in the new development of University Town Center. We are accessible from the Beltway and Interstates 495 and 95 near Montgomery County and Washington, D.C. and free parking is available.\r\n<h3>Contact Us</h3>\r\nTo get more information or to schedule an appointment with an experienced lawyer regarding a fatal injury from a police officer or a car accident, please contact us.', 'Wrongful Death', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'wrongful-death', '', '', '2014-03-05 06:51:56', '2014-03-05 06:51:56', '', '0', 'http://odelugojohnsonllc.com/?page_id=809', '0', 'page', '', '0');
