INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('900', '1', '2013-03-08 07:43:16', '2013-03-08 07:43:16', '<div>\r\n\r\nLightweight, pop-up hampers may seem at first glance to be convenient and safe, with the added benefit of collapsing to save space when not in use. However, the design of the hampers, with thin nylon fabric encasing a tightly coiled, strong spiral of metal, has resulted in a product that consumer advocates are calling \"emerging hazards.\"\r\n\r\nA woman suffered a gruesome and life-changing injury when the metal coil from her new hamper popped out of the packaging as she opened it, slicing through her right eye. Now completely blind in that eye, she\'s enlisted the help of a Houston attorney in suing the hampers\' manufacturers.\r\n\r\nSome of these hampers are designed for use by children or in children\'s rooms. A doctor examined two children-an 11-year-old boy and a 23-month-old girl-within a short period of time from each other, who were also injured in the eyes by the same type of hamper. The doctor realized a pattern with eye injuries caused by these hampers, and is concerned about the possible widespread risk to consumers. In fact, at least five people across the country have reported serious injury from pop-up hampers.\r\n\r\nThe Consumer Product Safety Commission (CPSC) is considering an investigation into the hampers. When a product causes permanent injury such as the woman who lost her eye, victims may be eligible for compensation. And when a product is dangerous enough to cause child injury, it\'s important to report the injury to the CPSC and consider speaking to a personal injury attorney about ways to prevent more people from becoming hurt by the dangerous product.\r\n\r\n<strong>Source</strong>: KHOU.com, \"<a href=\"http://www.khou.com/news/investigative/Hidden-Hazard-Injuring-Children-and-Others-Using-Pop-Up-Laundry-Hampers-191037741.html\" target=\"_blank\">Home \'laundry hampers\' injuring children\'s, adults\' eyesight</a>,\" Author, Feb. 13, 2013\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Pop-up hamper costs Houston woman her eye, injures children', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pop-up-hamper-costs-houston-woman-her-eye-injures-children', '', '', '2014-02-28 07:44:11', '2014-02-28 07:44:11', '', '0', 'http://odelugojohnsonllc.com/?p=900', '0', 'post', '', '0');
