INSERT INTO spk_posts VALUES('958', '1', '2013-07-25 10:06:09', '2013-07-25 10:06:09', '<div>\r\n\r\nReceiving a diagnosis of a clean bill of health after a cancer scare would seem like a new lease on life for most Maryland residents. However, it can be a traumatic experience even after finding out they are healthy and their lives arent in danger. Its even worse if treatment for cancer was already started. Many medical malpractice cases are filed on account of a doctors misdiagnosis of an illness, or even a failure to diagnose a healthy result.\r\n\r\nA 54-year-old woman from Texas was recently awarded $367,500 for physical pain and mental anguish, after shed received months of treatments for cancer she never had. Her doctor told her that she had State IV terminal breast cancer after having a benign tumor removed from her left breast. The woman underwent eight rounds of chemotherapy for seven months, while giving away her possessions and preparing to die.\r\n\r\nShe said she became severely depressed during her treatment, as well as suffered the usual physical effects of chemo, such as hair loss and extreme fatigue. After she sought treatment for anxiety, her new doctors surprised her by revealing her original doctor had misread her lab results, and she had never had cancer.\r\n\r\nAlthough she and her husband are happy that shes perfectly healthy, the woman says shell never be the same as a result of her misdiagnosis and chemotherapy treatments. The emotional damage that comes from a doctor error can be just as devastating as the physical damage, and victims are entitled to seek compensation.\r\n\r\n<b>Source:</b>KHOU 11 News, <a href=\"http://www.khou.com/news/health/Cancer-free-woman-undergoes-chemotherapy-after-false-diagnosis-215766391.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cancer-free woman undergoes chemotherapy after false diagnosis</a>, Drew Karedes, July 17, 2013\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Woman wins award after cancer misdiagnosis', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'woman-wins-award-after-cancer-misdiagnosis', '', '', '2014-02-28 10:07:21', '2014-02-28 10:07:21', '', '0', 'http://odelugojohnsonllc.com/?p=958', '0', 'post', '', '0');
